ContentDesc_Götterdämmerung - Sephirot: Sephirot, the Fiend, was a deity once worshipped by a treelike race native to Meracydia. Brought into being for the sole purpose of repelling the Allagan invasion, Sephirot inflicted ruinous losses upon the imperial army before finally being subdued and imprisoned in the central facility of Azys Lla. And now, millennia later, this immensely powerful entity threatens to awaken, his vengeful dreams disturbed by the careless ambitions of Archbishop Thordan VII. Topple the first pillar of the Warring Triad, or wheresoever his colossal shadow falls shall be visited by unthinkable catastrophe!
Instancecontenttextdata_9901_Text: Pestilent northerners...You shall regret the decision to loosen my fetters!
Instancecontenttextdata_9902_Text: The equilibrium of life...I shall tip thy scales and partake of thy bounteous energy!
Instancecontenttextdata_9903_Text: Patience and penance...For millennia have I yearned to enact this vengeance!
Instancecontenttextdata_9904_Text: I am the end and the beginning!By my touch shall your wretched lives be blessed!
Instancecontenttextdata_9905_Text: I am the incarnation of life!I cannot perish...cannot wither...
Instancecontenttextdata_9907_Text: You have dimmed my boundless light.What power of death do you mortals wield...?
